import React, {useState} from "react"
import { DropdownWrapper, Nav, CloseIcon, List, DropDownLink } from "./DropdownElements"

export const DropdownNav = () => {

    return(
        <DropdownWrapper>
            <Nav>
                <CloseIcon/>
            </Nav>
                <List>
                <Link to="/">Home</Link>
                <Link to="/">About Me</Link>
                <Link to="/">Work</Link>
                <Link to="/">Resume</Link>
                </List>
        </DropdownWrapper>
    )
}
